'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 7''' is the seventh issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 4|''Star Wars'' (1977) 4]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 1|Man-Gods from Beyond the Stars]]" {{C|Part 2}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 4|The Sword in the Star!: Stave 1: Alas, the Seeds of Man!]]" {{C|Part 3}}

*Letters Column with C-3PO
*"Lets Meet C3PO..." &mdash; An interview with [[Anthony Daniels]], conducted by Audrey Smith.
*Competition to win one of fifty "Escape from the Death Star" board games from Palitoy. To enter, readers must answer a five true-or-false questions relating to ''Star Wars''.

